<div id="pf4192" class="pf w53 h2f4" data-page-no="4192"><div class="pc pc4192 w53 h2f4"><div class="t m42e x0 h5 y2cd4 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 4 January 22-28 </div><div class="t m2430 xd3 h2e2 y2cca ff9 fs5b fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Scittaalti- </div><div class="t mea6 xb7 h2e2 y561 ff9 fs5b fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A </div><div class="t m19b6 x28 h2e2 ydf0 ff3 fs5b fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Alenioricil of </div><div class="t m1e13 xda h2e2 yf1f ff3 fs5b fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Cnzation </div><div class="t m2a6 x27 h5 ycaa ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Speak thou also unto the children </div><div class="t m324 xb9 h5 y1002 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of Israel, saying, Verily my sabbaths ye </div><div class="t m1ed xb9 h5 y15a7 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">shall keep: for it is a sign between me </div><div class="t m2c0 xb7 h5 yd70 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and you throughout your generations; </div><div class="t m5aa xb9 h5 y795 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that ye may know that I am the Lord </div><div class="t mac1 xb9 h5 ye48 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that doth sanctify you&quot; (Ex. 31:13). </div><div class="t mb6c x27 h35 y97e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Sabbath distinguishes the </div><div class="t m480 xb9 h35 y7d1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Seventh-day Adventist Church from </div><div class="t m1581 xb9 h35 yf2a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">many other Christian groups. Too </div><div class="t m119 xb9 h35 yb79 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">often we forget what a great influence </div><div class="t m110a xb9 h35 y10a8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Sabbath</div><div class="t m2165 x55 h35 y10a8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">-</div><div class="t m435 x53 h35 ya8f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">has been toward helping </div><div class="t m3af xb9 h35 y76c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">us be the kind of Christians we should </div><div class="t ma43 xb9 h35 ya13 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">be. Sometimes the fact that the </div><div class="t m3ad xb9 h35 ybd5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">observance of the seventh-day </div><div class="t m210 xb9 h35 y10eb ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sabbath sets Seventh-day Adventists </div><div class="t m589 xb9 h35 y1276 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">apart from other Christians becomes </div><div class="t ma6 xb9 h35 yf38 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">enlarged in our minds, and becomes </div><div class="t m485 xb9 h35 ydb6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">an end in itself, a form of salvation by </div><div class="t m22e xb9 h35 y726 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">works. But the keeping of the Sabbath </div><div class="t mf4 xb9 h35 yece ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cannot save a person any more than </div><div class="t m79d xb9 h35 y962 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">any other works can save. If the </div><div class="t m70d xb9 h35 ydfe ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">observance of this special day does </div><div class="t mbbe xb9 h35 yd9b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">not bring us into closer fellowship </div><div class="t ma43 xb9 h35 y90c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">with our Creator and give us greater </div><div class="t m1a4 xb9 h35 yffb ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">insights into His love, power, and </div><div class="t m589 xb9 h35 y118e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">redeeming grace, the Sabbath&apos;will </div><div class="t m8d9 xb9 h35 yf49 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">have failed to accomplish God&apos;s </div><div class="t m15a8 xb9 h35 y15fd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">intentions for us. </div><div class="t mddb x27 h35 yd45 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The seventh-day Sabbath is a sign </div><div class="t ma8c xb9 h35 ydbc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">which God intends His people to </div><div class="t m192 x3 h35 yf50 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">carry. It is a sign which informs those </div><div class="t m98a xb9 h35 y188f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">who observe us that we believe in God </div><div class="t m2436 xb9 h5 ycb7 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">as </div><div class="t m2be x11 h35 ycb7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Creator and that this Creator God is </div><div class="t m4d6 xb9 h5 ya9b ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">worthy </div><div class="t m228f x29 h35 ya9b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of our worship. The </div><div class="t m2d2 xb9 h35 yce4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">importance of this sign will increase as </div><div class="t m1a18 xda h35 y9fe ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">.welcome to the close of earth&apos;s </div><div class="t m971 xb9 h35 yd68 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">hikory. Let us carry this sign not only </div><div class="t m737 x3 h35 yc89 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">with humility but also with </div><div class="t m7c5 x3 h35 ye16 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">responsibility and dignity in such a </div><div class="t m3c6 x3 h35 y12e2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">way that it will cause our neighbors  </div><div class="t m7ca x8f h35 y106a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and those with whom we associate to </div><div class="t m11c x8f h35 y1002 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">desire a saving relationship with the </div><div class="t mdd1 x8f h35 y1098 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">heavenly Father. </div><div class="t m4ff xb0 h35 yd70 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Creator did not need to set apart </div><div class="t m83c x8f h35 y795 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">a day for rest after His work of </div><div class="t m2af x8f h35 ye48 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Creation. But He saw that man would </div><div class="t m5d4 x8f h35 y97e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">need such a day. In His loving </div><div class="t m7b5 x8f h35 y7d1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">forethought He established this day </div><div class="t ma87 x8f h35 yd04 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that we might be able to rest our weary </div><div class="t m30a x8f h35 ybb3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">bodies after the days of labor and that </div><div class="t m490 x8f h35 y10a8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">we might find spiritual refreshing in </div><div class="t m591 x8f h35 y76c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the contemplation of the Creator and </div><div class="t m11b x8f h35 ycd6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">His works. </div><div class="t m4d6 x72 h5 yf33 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m23f x72 h5 y139a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m5c5 xbc h5 y139b ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Sabbath Established </div><div class="t me9f xbc h5 yd77 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Gen. 2:1, 2) </div><div class="t m558 x72 h5 ycad ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m45d xbc h5 y526 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Purpose </div><div class="t me3e xbc h5 y1329 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Eze. 20:20) </div><div class="t mb7 x72 h5 y844 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m631 xbc h5 y844 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Basis of Worship </div><div class="t m5e0 xbc h5 ye10 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Neh. 9:6) </div><div class="t m1ce x72 h5 yee5 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t mdc8 xbc h5 y963 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A Bulwark Against Error </div><div class="t m847 xbc h5 ybba ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Jer. 10:14-10 </div><div class="t m8a8 x72 h5 yd9c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m34f xbc h5 y1266 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God Is Creator </div><div class="t m211 xbc h5 y478 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 4:11) </div><div class="t m2ef x72 h5 y12d9 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m2bb xbc h5 y12d9 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A Sabbath for Eternity </div><div class="t m4cd xbc h5 y66f ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Isa. 66:22, 23) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
